{"tid":1656692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輔仁容總親自教路如何做FB假截圖","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:33:59.000Z","uid":47437,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f7a4fbadda249da9c1436c0fbccc039ca121b4","tid":1656692,"uid":47437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/10/16/200096#%E3%80%90%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AC%9B%E5%9C%B0%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A2%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%9C%E6%89%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2019%2F10%2F16%2F200096%23%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25BD%2586&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e0bc819c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/10/16/200096#%E3%80%90%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AC%9B%E5%9C%B0%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A2%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%9C%E6%89%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86</a><br />\n<br />\n建制派網媒旗艦話，呢個係陳彥霖嘅媽媽，佢出post 求大家停手，俾佢個女安息。<br />\n<br />\n我唔講其他野，今次同上次我講警察睇大波妹一樣，純粹分享技術層面來講，一張cap 圖就作故仔，係可以幾咁唔可信。<br />\n<br />\n首先求其搵一個有字嘅post。<br />\n真係求其得架喇，因為之後可以改到所有野唔同。<br />\n（對唔住大佬！反正你地球post！）<br />\n<br />\n用Chrome 打開開發人員工具<br />\n<br />\n點選網頁元素模式<br />\n<br />\n改名，任你改的，叫咩都得。<br />\n<br />\n改時間，都係任你改，你改未來時間都得，只係一堆字。<br />\n<br />\n改文字，又係任你改。<br />\n<br />\n改完，記住cap 圖，用唔曬個版面唔緊要架，你cap 要嘅部份咪得。<br />\n<br />\n大家務必留意，呢種玩法，一定只會得張圖，因為呢個post 從來都無喺facebook 個server 出現過，所以唔會俾你搵到。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者可能會問，如果真係有個acc 出post 呢？<br />\n咁就仲簡單，去開個email，註冊一個新嘅fb 帳號，叫咩名都得，寫咩都得，截圖，有link 添，有無人信就另一回事。<br />\n<br />\n霞姨呢個有飯盒：）<br />\n<br />\n然後看圖作文。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係完全唔相信佢阿媽會叫大家收手，而係港人講地如果真係知道佢阿媽嘅下落同埋意願，好應該訪問佢，就算唔出樣，影住佢背面做示意圖片都好丫，你求其一個fb 截圖，我都截到俾你架。<br />\n你要幾多張都得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再一次希望讀者，唔好再信所謂嘅fb 截圖。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有喺個網頁出現嘅野，都可以偽造然後截圖。<br />\n人係要長大。<br />\n<br />\n（啲圖唔copy過嚟啦自己睇啦）"},{"pid":"c9d94c779ea53c5c944f0422c83103584ec4003a","tid":1656692,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9e706a7752676fd9b090d45791327204c698f44a","tid":1656692,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75dd37124b98a35cc3554ea4173580ae839fe9d2","tid":1656692,"uid":47437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"c4fc512a314e65c482643bc623ddde3c2be4e060","tid":1656692,"uid":47437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"a8eb8f70966aac92f868155c77a0fb97911b2c14","tid":1656692,"uid":47437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"d4d9b8adbff5c8c1065d989491b069596026f04c","tid":1656692,"uid":47437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"3c27f1ddb022f3a0ef65cb9e544cdf70c849045a","tid":1656692,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhphm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn